2. Midline vertical incision about 6 cm . Exposure of L4 - S1laminar after bilateral PVM splitting .

3. Bilateral hemilaminectomy of L4 & L5 with facetectomy were done and bilatral L5 & S1 roots were identified and decompressed . Severe stenosis of L4-5 & L5 / S1 level was noted . Satisfactory decompression was achieved bilaterally .
4. After identification of L4 , L5 and S1 pedicles , pedicle screw were inserted in each pedicle .
5. L4-5 & L5 / S1 discectomy was done with currate and pit rongeur . Two intervertebral cages were inserted in each side of L4-5 & L5 / S1 intervertebral space .
6. Hemostant and antiadhesive agent , Inogram and Gelform was apply .
6. After checking of intraop X - ray , the wound was closed layer by layer remaing the drain .
